      • calculateConfidenceIntervalsForRAM

        public void calculateConfidenceIntervalsForRAM(Host currentHost)
        This procedure calculates the utilization measures of the device RAM. RAM utilization is calculated for all the host and all the softServres deployed on that host.
        Parameters:
        currentHost - : current host for which utilization is to be calculated Assumption : Busy and idle threads consumes the same amount of memory
